data.description: Welcome to the Lake! Experience full-time lake living or a quick weekend getaway. This welcoming home is nestled on a 0.56 acre lot in a peaceful neighborhood 4 minutes past Buffalo Shores. The open kitchen and living concept is perfect for entertaining with plenty of room for your family and friends. Outside enjoy coffee on the large expansive deck in the morning with the peaceful surroundings. Play in the lake with easy lake-front access and a public ramp for neighborhood use. Access Walmart, Harps and Grove's downtown community within minutes. The home features three bedrooms, two full bathrooms and one half bathroom.
